its not a surprise. Just go with them to the freaking plane and help them clear it. <br>
<br>
For as much baby eating as they do, they're still pretty reasonable people when talked to *politely*<br>
<br>
Now I've had my fair share of being flamed and acting irrationally back to CQ members, usually because I try to ride the line in the middle. I know where they are and how they view things, and it isn't how I view them, but at least they let you know ahead of time. It isn't a hidden agenda to screw over guilds X, Y, and Z. They're all people too, and most of them are pretty reasonable. Some of them are jerks, some of them are nice, just like every guild. <br>
<br>
in short, just realize they're going to do what they want to when they want to, and more often than not, it doesn't interfere with anyone else in the game. When it does, they're pretty reasonable with people who come to them with an alternate setup on how they want to do something that appeases both parties.<br>
&lt;shrug&gt;<br>
